## Cycle 8 — Architecture audit & production hardening
- **Task:** Comprehensive audit + full improvement roadmap + implementation across all Critical/High/Medium/Low findings
- **Owner:** Orchestrator-led multi-agent (Architect, Developer, QA, Documentation)
- **Status:** Complete
- **Key deliverables:**
  - **C1** Atomic service operations — `JdbcTxRunner` with commit/rollback; `addTransaction`, `deleteTransaction`, `updateTransaction` are fully atomic
  - **C2** Connection infrastructure — single static connection replaced with HikariCP pool + ThreadLocal `ConnectionContext` + `java.sql`-free `TxRunner` interface; `DataAccessException` (unchecked); `Repositories` factory; `DirectTxRunner` test double
  - **C3** Cross-currency fix — destination credited with `amount.multiply(exchangeRate).setScale(4, HALF_EVEN)` (was crediting raw source amount)
  - **C4** Secrets removed from VCS — `config.properties` gitignored; env-var-first (`BT_DB_URL/USER/PASSWORD`); `config.properties.example` with placeholders
  - **H1** Recurrence timezone — `LocalDate.now(ZoneId.of(rule.getZoneId()))` per rule inside loop
  - **H2** Variable income — `TxStatus {PENDING, POSTED, CANCELLED}` on `transactions`; `confirmPending` / `cancelPending` service methods
  - **H3** Ownership enforcement — userId validated on all mutating service operations
  - **H4** Logging — SLF4J 2.0.16 + Logback 1.5.12; all catch-blocks log before throwing
  - **H5** Input validation — email regex, password length ≥8, currency `[A-Z]{3}`, amount >0, date not null
  - **M1** Budget alerts surfaced — WARN/OVER envelopes shown in Dashboard Home + Budgets screen
  - **M3** Edit-transaction — `updateTransaction` with full account/category deduplication and re-evaluation
  - **M5** Flyway migrations — V1 (schema), V2 (transfer_account_id index), V3 (status column); `baselineOnMigrate=true`
  - **L1** README.md — 10-section setup/run guide
  - **L2** GitHub Actions CI — `.github/workflows/ci.yml` (MySQL 8 service, Oracle Java 25)
  - **L3** nbactions.xml gitignored
  - **L4** ARCHITECTURE.md patched (javafx.version, BudgetStatus, TxStatus enum values)
  - **L5** module-info.java deferred (jbcrypt/flyway-core/mysql-connector-j have no Automatic-Module-Name); classpath mode documented in pom.xml
